## Dependency Injection Wiring

```
user-service.ts (composition root)
│
├── Creates: new UserRepositoryImpl()
│   └── Implements: UserRepository interface (domain)
│   └── Delegates to: userApi (axios calls)
│
└── Wires use cases with repository:
    ├── new GetUsersUseCase(repo)
    ├── new GetUserByIdUseCase(repo)
    ├── new CreateUserUseCase(repo)
    ├── new UpdateUserUseCase(repo)
    └── new DeleteUserUseCase(repo)

Consumed by presentation hooks:
    useUsers()       → userService.getUsers.execute(params)
    useUser()        → userService.getUserById.execute(id)
    useCreateUser()  → userService.createUser.execute(data)
    useUpdateUser()  → userService.updateUser.execute(id, data)
    useDeleteUser()  → userService.deleteUser.execute(id)
```

